quote><br />\n廚房佬可能因為老細刻薄唔請夠人，咁是咪要轉去屌鳩老細?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n老細都唔想,最衰就係舖租貴,應該去屌個地主"},{"pid":"234d2eec57d1c930c9d87c7f129a1dcac8f71524","tid":107420,"uid":14921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:43:02.000Z","msg":"係咪你樣問題<br />\n我上次去 我一開波狂落order <br />\n佢同我勁快嚟哂 我地食唔切 二人枱放唔哂添"},{"pid":"c23b82f5d6e4c7ac1e236351373fedcc6b69f9cc","tid":107420,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:44:00.000Z","msg":"又要做放題 又要死慳死抵諗埋啲度叔數 真係少啲面子先做到個度啲員工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fa00f3f630029eb687791740c1f88ebbca8aa2e","tid":107420,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:46:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"71c8d26404a93fcb5fd9eab20da7a0caf7e1cf90","tid":107420,"uid":59679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:55:05.000Z","msg":"但係.... 任嗌嫁喎"},{"pid":"7d0f45992d9395cb56cfca3834400b3e8f0dcf46","tid":107420,"uid":32887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T17:19:07.000Z","msg":"我係尖沙咀食又黎得幾快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然都係黎唔足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42b9f79d994cc3396c419eca9430369bbb7d1cad","tid":107420,"uid":1790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T17:35:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係咪你樣問題<br />\n我上次去 我一開波狂落order <br />\n佢同我勁快嚟哂 我地食唔切 二人枱放唔哂添</blockquote><br />\n關咩事<br />\n每日廚房人手未必穩定咖嘛<br />\n如果有個散工甩底嘅　情況已經差好撚遠啦<br />\n總之佢畀氣waiter受就on9啦　條友仲要好似好威咁講出嚟　弱智</blockquote><br />\n痴線 waiter大過客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1812b7bab07d583fe42ded204bb4f986f40fd6a","tid":107420,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T17:37:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d4ba8df0b04f30b4afb3351ca9a2b849f5b913bd","tid":107420,"uid":19979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T17:40:03.000Z","msg":"樓主有冇狂落單先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw 食過兩三次 d野食都好快黎齊<br />\n樓主唔好彩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"515eca26f31205300d89bd3906c80953e447ffea","tid":107420,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T17:41:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ab0e98ce1c5557a057a8798d42990dff09cb39f1","tid":107420,"uid":47029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T17:42:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係咪你樣問題<br />\n我上次去 我一開波狂落order <br />\n佢同我勁快嚟哂 我地食唔切 二人枱放唔哂添</blockquote><br />\n關咩事<br />\n每日廚房人手未必穩定咖嘛<br />\n如果有個散工甩底嘅　情況已經差好撚遠啦<br />\n總之佢畀氣waiter受就on9啦　條友仲要好似好威咁講出嚟　弱智</blockquote><br />\n痴線 waiter大過客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你咩理解能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 曲解？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁落單又係waiter，催單又係要搵waiter，waiter既存在就係要服務客人幫個客搞掂佢啦， 幫唔到個客唔屌waiter屌邊個"},{"pid":"4d8dcd2688d790b5173a8277bf91a05b07c82be5","tid":107420,"uid":76423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T17:53:35.000Z","msg":"痴線 雖然我做過waiter都知有d出餐慢係因為廚房事<br />\n催佢地會比班廚房佬燥<br />\n但係比客催單都算幾合理啦 依家係一個鐘唔係10分鐘"},{"pid":"b997f98f034ff8de1161c5b464545b50b2a4833d","tid":107420,"uid":1790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T17:54:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n痴線 waiter大過客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你咩理解能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 曲解？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁落單又係waiter，催單又係要搵waiter，waiter既存在就係要服務客人幫個客搞掂佢啦， 幫唔到個客唔屌waiter屌邊個</blockquote><br />\n一個鐘冇野食都唔屌得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nWaiter真係好野"}]}